FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 4, product_id: 6, additional_info: "Nest offers one of the easiest set ups in the security camera market. You can view a live feed of the camera(s) from your phone, tablet, or computer and even record video for later review. Also available is a discounted pack of 3 cameras or a combination of 1 indoor and 1 outdoor camera, to give you an even greater sense of safety and security, from anywhere in the world.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 4, product_id: 7, additional_info: "The D-Link Pan and Tilt camera is another great option, which allows you to move the camera around from your phone, tablet, or computer to provide a more dynamic viewing area. ")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 4, product_id: 8, additional_info: "The D-Link Video Recorder will allow you to store the video from your D-Link camera safely in your home rather than on the cloud, so that you can be sure your security is private.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 5, product_id: 6, additional_info: "Nest offers one of the easiest set ups in the security camera market. You can view a live feed of the camera(s) from your phone, tablet, or computer and even store video online for later review, for a small fee. Also available is a discounted pack of 3 cameras or a combination of 1 indoor and 1 outdoor camera, to give you an even greater sense of safety and security, from anywhere in the world.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 5, product_id: 7, additional_info: "The D-Link Pan and Tilt camera is another great option, which allows you to move the camera around from your phone, tablet, or computer to provide a more dynamic viewing area. ")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 5, product_id: 9, additional_info: "The D-Link Day and Night Wifi camera is another great option for home security. With the same remote viewing capabilities of the Nest or other D-Link cameras, this camera is simple to install and set up. ")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 5, product_id: 8, additional_info: "The D-Link Video Recorder will allow you to store the video from your D-Link camera safely in your home rather than on the cloud, so that you can be sure your security is private.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 6, product_id: 10, additional_info: "August smart locks are a great investment for controlling the access to your home. With a fully functional mobile application and support with systems such as SmartThings, the August locks allow you to control your door locks from anywhere in the world. Never forget to lock the door again, and never worry if your kids forget their keys.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 36, product_id: 11, additional_info: "The SmartThings Home Monitoring kit is really an amazing introductory security setup for anyone interested in smart homes. In addition to the motion sensor and contact sensors, you also get a SmartThings Hub, which means you can add hundreds of devices to your system, including non-security items, without having to worry.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 7, product_id: 12, additional_info: "The Ring Video Doorbell is probably the most versatile smart doorbell on the market, especially for the price. With high quality audio and video transmission, not only can you ensure your home's safety, you can also ensure that no package goes undelivered, that the kids are home, and more.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 8, product_id: 15, additional_info: "The SONOS PLAY:1 speakers are great for easy distributed audio throughout the home. They link up to your WiFi and allow you to choose which speakers you would like to use. Higher versions (such as the PLAY:5) allow for higher sound quality.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 8, product_id: 14, additional_info: "For larger houses, or houses where the WiFi signal doesn't reach certain rooms you want to play music in, the SONOS BOOST allows you to connect the SONOS speakers to eachother, instead of directly to the WiFi network, meaning you can greatly extend their potential range.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 9, product_id: 17, additional_info: "The Logitech Harmony remotes are the undisputed champions of universal remotes, and this one includes a fully functional touch screen that allows you to use customized controls on up to 15 different devices. This model even features the ability to control home automation devices, such as the SmartThings Hub.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 10, product_id: 13, additional_info: "The Denon AVRX4300H is one of the best receivers on the market. It includes full Bluetooth and Wi-Fi capabilities, giving you the power to control all of your home theater equipment from your phone or other smart devices.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 11, product_id: 16, additional_info: "The new Amazon Fire Stick allows you to access a truly massive collection of tv shows, movies, and music. When it comes to all-in-one media devices, the Fire Stick is touch to beat.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 12, product_id: 16, additional_info: "The new Amazon Fire Stick allows you to access a truly massive collection of tv shows, movies, and music. When it comes to all-in-one media devices, the Fire Stick is touch to beat. Additionally, the new version comes with a voice control through the remote to make the use of the system that much easier and more accessible.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 13, product_id: 18, additional_info: "The Nucleus Anywhere Intercoms are a really great gift for family and friends alike. They allow for instantaneous voice and video communication from another Nucleus tablet or directly from your smart phone. Additionally, they include music, news, weather, and other capabilities, such as a Do Not Disturb mode which even allows you to shutter the camera.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 14, product_id: 20, additional_info: "The Amazon Echo is easily the best voice-controlled smart home controller on the market. The full Echo includes a powerful speaker system inside the tower and can respond to commands to control hundreds of devices. Once you have the Echo, you can control nearly any other device on this site with it.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 14, product_id: 21, additional_info: "The Amazon Echo Dot is very similar to the Amazon Echo. In order to reduce cost and size, Amazon essentially has just removed the speaker system that was built into the full-sized Echo. The Echo and the Echo Dots can communicate across the house as well, so feel free to place several dots around the home for maximum control!")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 15, product_id: 22, additional_info: "The Honeywell Lyric T5 is the best smart thermostat for the money on the market right now. It is extremely easy to program and use, and it can be integrated with Siri, Amazon Alexa, and Apple HomeKit among other smart systems. One of the coolest features is the advanced geofencing, which can detect when you are on your way home if you have the app installed and can have the house the perfect temperature for you when you get there, without wasting energy all day to keep the temperature when nobody is home.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 15, product_id: 27, additional_info: "Easily the most well-known smart thermostat on the market, the Nest thermostat earns its reputation as the most reliable, most advanced smart thermostat out there. It's a bit more expensive than the Lyric T5, but it is extremely easy to use and has the best design of any thermostat on the market. It includes all of the features of the Lyric T5 and more, including an advanced AI that can learn your schedule and adjust your temperatures without making you set a schedule explicitly.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 16, product_id: 12, additional_info: "The Ring Wi-Fi Enabled Video Doorbell has the ability to interface with a ton of other devices to let you know that someone is at the door. It can detect motion, or when the doorbell is rung. For those hard of hearing, or just those listening to their music too loud, the Ring Doorbell, combined with the IFTTT app can flash your lights, pause your music, or alert you in another way so that you never miss that important delivery.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 16, product_id: 1, additional_info: "This Hue kit contains 3 full-color lights and can be integrated with the Ring Doorbell through the IFTTT app to blink the lights to let you know someone is at the door. You can even have it flash a specific color to distinguish between alerts. ")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 16, product_id: 2, additional_info: "If needed, these are the Hue full-color bulbs to expand the Hue Bridge kits so you can control even more lights throughout the house.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 16, product_id: 3, additional_info: "This Hue Kit contains 3 white lights and can be integrated with the Ring Doorbell through the IFTTT app to blink the lights to let you know someone is at the door. ")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 16, product_id: 4, additional_info: "If needed, these are the Hue white bulbs to expand the Hue Bridge kits so you can control even more lights throughout the house.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 17, product_id: 23, additional_info: "The Samsung SmartThings leak detection sensor can be placed anywhere through the home to alert you if there is water somewhere it shouldn't be. Place them near your washer, your water heater, that one leaky spot in the basement, or anywhere you want to monitor for water. In order to communicate with the sensor, you'll also need the SmartThings Hub, which allows you to expand and integrate more devices into your system as you desire.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 17, product_id: 24, additional_info: "The SmartThings Hub is the main brain of the SmartThings brand of smart home automation systems. It is extremely easy to set up, can send alerts directly to your phone, and is compatible with hudreds of devices, allowing you to grow your smart home at the pace most comfortable for you.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 18, product_id: 26, additional_info: "The SmartThings outlet allows you to control the power to lamps, small appliances, and other electronics. Use it to monitor the energy usage of your TV, control lamps in an office, or anything else you can think of. In order to communicate with the outlet, you'll also need the SmartThings Hub, which allows you to expand and integrate more devices into your system as you desire.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 18, product_id: 24, additional_info: "The SmartThings Hub is the main brain of the SmartThings brand of smart home automation systems. It is extremely easy to set up, can send alerts directly to your phone, and is compatible with hudreds of devices, allowing you to grow your smart home at the pace most comfortable for you.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 19, product_id: 25, additional_info: "The Leak Gopher Water Control Valve allows you to protect your home from unfortunate water leaks from burst pipes, busted appliances, or even the kids leaving a sink running. Combined with a Z-Wave smart hub, such as the SmartThings Hub, the Leak Gopher Water Control Valve can, for example, save you thousands of dollars in repairs by turning off the main water line to the house in the event a leak is detected on a SmartThings Water Leak Detector. Important Note!: Make sure you choose the right size for your home's main water line! If you aren't sure what size you need, consult a plumber to be sure.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 19, product_id: 23, additional_info: "The Samsung SmartThings leak detection sensor can be placed anywhere through the home to alert you if there is water somewhere it shouldn't be. Place them near your washer, your water heater, that one leaky spot in the basement, or anywhere you want to monitor for water. In order to communicate with the sensor, you'll also need the SmartThings Hub, which allows you to expand and integrate more devices into your system as you desire.")
