FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 21, product_id: 28, additional_info: "Aeon Labs' Home Energy meter connects safely and easily, directly to the main breaker box. This allows you to track the total energy usage of your entire home, so that you can be sure you are getting the maximum savings from your new smart home. Connect it to your SmartThings Hub to monitor and track energy usage in your home to reduce your carbon footprint (and your bills!).")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 21, product_id: 26, additional_info: "The SmartThings outlet allows you to control the power to lamps, small appliances, and other electronics. Use it to monitor the energy usage of your TV, control lamps in an office, or anything else you can think of. In order to communicate with the outlet, you'll also need the SmartThings Hub, which allows you to expand and integrate more devices into your system as you desire.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 21, product_id: 1, additional_info: "This kit includes the Hue Bridge and 3 of their newest generation of full-color Hue Bulbs for the best colors and control of your lighting. LED bulbs like the Samsung Hue use up to 80% less power than stabdard incandescent bulbs, which can save you money and reduce your carbon footprint.")
