FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 22, product_id: 27, additional_info: "Easily the most well-known smart thermostat on the market, the Nest thermostat earns its reputation as the most reliable, most advanced smart thermostat out there. It is extremely easy to use and has the best design of any thermostat on the market. It includes a wealth of amazing features, including an advanced AI that can learn your schedule and adjust your temperatures without making you set a schedule explicitly. Combined with the SmartThings Hub and the SmartThings outlet, you can censerve even more energy by only powering fans and other appliances when the temperature reaches a certain threshhold.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 23, product_id: 30, additional_info: "This H2o Vibe Showerhead has a built-in bluetooth speaker so you can jam out to all your favorite tunes without worrying about damaging your phone.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 24, product_id: 31, additional_info: "The Rachio Smart Sprinkler Controller gives you the ultimate control over your sprinkler system. It can be combined with other smart systems, such as SmartThings and Amazon Echo, to help you preserve water and take the best care of your lawn, without having to worry about turning on the sprinklers every day.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 25, product_id: 31, additional_info: "The Rachio Smart Sprinkler Controller gives you the ultimate control over your sprinkler system. It can be combined with other smart systems, such as SmartThings and Amazon Echo, to help you preserve water and take the best care of your lawn, without having to worry about turning on the sprinklers every day. Simply add a weather check with SmartThings or Alexa to disable the sprinklers if the forecast shows rain and you're all set to go!")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 26, product_id: 32, additional_info: "The WORX Landroid is the Roomba of lawns. This intelligent, self-driven lawnmower will take care of your grass for you, so you can enjoy your days instead.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 27, product_id: 33, additional_info: "The Edyn Garden Sensor can be placed in your garden or flowerbed to keep track of the moisture, light, temperature, and nutrient levels of the soil so you can ensure your plants will be the envy of the neighborhood.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 28, product_id: 34, additional_info: "The Invoxia Smart Portable Speaker is designed for rugged outdoor use. It features voice commands with Amazon Alexa, internet radio through services like Pandora and Spotify, and can even act as a speakerphone for a phone connected via Bluetooth.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 29, product_id: 15, additional_info: "The SONOS PLAY:1 speakers are great for easy distributed audio throughout the home. They link up to your WiFi and allow you to choose which speakers you would like to use. Higher versions (such as the PLAY:5) allow for higher sound quality.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 29, product_id: 14, additional_info: "For larger houses, or houses where the WiFi signal doesn't reach certain rooms you want to play music in, the SONOS BOOST allows you to connect the SONOS speakers to eachother, instead of directly to the WiFi network, meaning you can greatly extend their potential range.")
FeatureProduct.create(feature_id: 29, product_id: 35, additional_info: "Another great option for distributed audio without all the wires is the Bose Soundtouch system. This package comes with 2 incredible Bose speakers that can be connected together wirelessly through your home Wi-Fi so you can play music from your phone or computer throughout the home.")
